a_warfare.jei.info.diamond_steel_bluepri: Can be obtained from Wandering Traders,Asgharian Dungeons or Ancient Cities

enchantment.a_warfare.quick_hands.desc: Increases the speed of reloading weapons
enchantment.a_warfare.trigger_finger.des: Increases the speed you can fire weapons
enchantment.a_warfare.lightweight.desc: Reduces the weight of a weapon to increase ADS speed
enchantment.a_warfare.collateral.desc: Makes fired bullets travel through multiple entities
enchantment.a_warfare.reclaimed.desc: Creates a chance that a bullet won't be consumed upon firing a weapon
enchantment.a_warfare.accelerator.desc: Increases the speed of fired projectiles causing them to do more damage
enchantment.a_warfare.puncturing.desc: Creates a chance that a bullet will deal critical damage
enchantment.a_warfare.fire_starter.desc: Fired bullets will set blocks and entities on fire upon impact
enchantment.a_warfare.shell_catcher.desc: Increases the amount of spent shells retrieved when firing.
enchantment.a_warfare.banzai.desc: Increases damage multiplier based off speed during Banzai.
enchantment.a_warfare.heavy_shot.desc: Increases damage, But lowers fire rate and shot speed.
enchantment.a_warfare.hot_barrel.desc: Firing fills a draining bar, the bars level increases damage and fire rate, and heavily increases recoil and weapon spread.
enchantment.a_warfare.elemental_pop.desc: Fired bullets will have a chance to inflict a variety of status effects
enchantment.a_warfare.waterproof.desc: Reduces the damage to weapons when firing underwater

a_warfare.category.workbench.title: Assembling
a_warfare.jei.info.repair_kit: Can be used to repair guns on an anvil
a_warfare.jei.info.copper_blueprint: Can be obtained from Gunsmith Villagers
a_warfare.jei.info.iron_blueprint: Can be obtained from Gunsmith Villagers or Dungeons
a_warfare.jei.info.piglin_blueprint: Can be obtained from Nether Bastions
a_warfare.jei.info.ocean_blueprint: Can be obtained from Buried Treasure
a_warfare.jei.info.deep_dark_blueprint: Can be obtained from Ancient Cities
a_warfare.jei.info.end_blueprint: Can be obtained from End Cities
a_warfare.jei.info.niter_glass: Power with Redstone to change transparency
a_warfare.jei.info.vent_collector: Place on top of a Geothermal Vent to collect Niter, or on a Sulfuric Vent to obtain Sulfur. Accepts Wool and Composite filters as filter items.
a_warfare.jei.info.lightning_battery: Can be used to store energy, and obtain plasma or shock cells. Can be charged with FE power, or by placing a lightning rod, on top, and striking with lightning
a_warfare.jei.info.lightning_rod_connect: Can be used to transfer the charged state of a lightning rod to a lightning battery
a_warfare.jei.info.pistol_ammo_box: Can store Compact Copper Rounds, Compact Advanced Rounds, and Hog Rounds
a_warfare.jei.info.rifle_ammo_box: Can store Standard Copper Rounds, Advanced Rounds, Gibbs Rounds, and Krāhg Rounds
a_warfare.jei.info.shotgun_ammo_box: Can store Shotgun Shells, Shulkshot and Bearpack Shells
a_warfare.jei.info.magnum_ammo_box: Can store Ramrod Rounds and Beowulf Rounds
a_warfare.jei.info.energy_ammo_box: Can store Energy Cells, Sculk Cells, Shock Cells and Blaze Fuel
a_warfare.jei.info.special_ammo_box: Can store Powder and Ball and Grapeshot
a_warfare.jei.info.empty_casing_pouch: Can be used to store casing and will catch spent casings
a_warfare.jei.info.rock_pouch: Can be used to store rocks
a_warfare.jei.info.dishes_pouch: Can be used to store your dirty dishes
a_warfare.jei.info.creative_ammo_box: Gives infinite ammo for all guns
a_warfare.jei.info.cryoniter: Inserting Niter/Cold items will freeze surrounding Water blocks
a_warfare.jei.info.thermolith: Inserting Vehement Coal/Extremely hot fuel items will melt surrounding rock to lava
a_warfare.jei.info.penetrator: A shaped charge, will explode a 3x3 tunnel in the direction its facing
a_warfare.jei.info.basic_turret: Must be powered via redstone, and have a Targeting module connected. Accepts Standard Copper Rounds, Advanced Rounds and Gibbs Rounds.
a_warfare.jei.info.auto_turret: Must be powered via redstone, and have a Targeting module connected. Accepts Compact Copper Rounds, Compact Advanced Rounds and Hog Rounds.
a_warfare.jei.info.shotgun_turret: Must be powered via redstone, and have a Targeting module connected. Accepts Shotgun Shells and Bearpack Shells.
a_warfare.jei.info.hostile_turret_target: Must be connected to a turret. Will target hostile mobs within range
a_warfare.jei.info.player_turret_targeti: Must be connected to a turret. Will target non-owner Players within range
a_warfare.jei.info.turret_targeting_bloc: Must be connected to a turret. Will target all non-owner mobs within range
a_warfare.jei.info.fire_rate_turret_modu: Must be connected to a turret. Will increase the fire rate of the turret
a_warfare.jei.info.damage_turret_module: Must be connected to a turret. Will increase the damage of the turret
a_warfare.jei.info.ammo_turret_module: Must be connected to a turret. Acts as a hopper will supply turrets inventory
a_warfare.jei.info.range_turret_module: Must be connected to a turret. Will increase the range of the turret
a_warfare.jei.info.shell_catcher_turret_: Must be connected to a turret. Will increase the chance of retrieving spent casings to 100%
a_warfare.jei.info.ancient_brass: Can be used in place of Brass, or used to tame Supply Scamps
a_warfare.jei.info.scamp_controller: Used to link a Supply Scamp to a container, or to change the behavior of a Supply Scamp, via shift right clicking
a_warfare.jei.info.enemy_log: Used to whitelist mobs a turret will fire at. Right click a mob to have the turrets fire at just that mob, Shift right click to whitelist that whole mob type.
a_warfare.jei.info.team_log: Used to blacklist mobs a turret will fire at. Right click a mob to have the turrets ignore just that mob, Shift right click to blacklist that whole mob type.
a_warfare.jei.info.niter_dust: Can be obtained from Geothermal vents, or composting in a Advanced Composter. Used in Gunpowder production, or as a weak fertilizer
a_warfare.jei.info.advanced_composter: Accepts compostable items to produce bone meal, phosphor dust and niter dust
a_warfare.jei.info.blasphemy: Can be obtained from using an Empty Blasphemy on a Blaze spawner.
